Package com.varukha.webproject.model.dao

package com.varukha.webproject.model.dao
This is DAO package. New contracts for interaction with MySQL database are specified here. Contain next contracts to Implement: AddressFirstDAO, AddressSecondDAO, DeliveryDAO, InvoiceDAO, OrderDAO, UserDAO, Contain SQL_Queries class to interaction implemented methods with MySQL database.
Version:
1.0
Author:
